area_color = Color(0.25, 0.42, 1, 0.3)
active_on_event = "read_notepad_2"
is_notepad = true
notepad_title = "Boss 3 Field Note"
notepad_content = "[b]Boss 3 / Memory Anchor[/b]

The third entity does not guard the arena. It guards a memory.
When it falls, A.V.A may be pulled into an archived scene that rewrites the route for a moment.

Test order:
1. Defeat Boss 3.
2. Let A.V.A walk to the cutscene point.
3. Click through each image and text fragment.
4. Confirm the memory deletion message appears before control returns."
notepad_event_target = "third_notepad"

[node name="NotepadAreaFinal" parent="." unique_id=1877903776 instance=ExtResource("3_4dtv0")]
position = Vector2(575, 545)
require_interact = true
action_name = "Read"
area_color = Color(0.02, 0.02, 0.02, 0.45)
active_on_event = "read_final_notepad"
is_notepad = true
notepad_title = "Final Note: Mother"
notepad_content = "[b]Final Note / Mother[/b]

The final signal identifies itself as Mother.
This is not only a battle target. It is a choice about what A.V.A becomes after the truth is restored.

After Mother falls, listen before choosing."
notepad_event_target = "final_notepad"

