area_color = Color(1, 0.7411765, 0.18039216, 0)
active_on_event = "read_notepad_1"
is_notepad = true
notepad_title = "📓 Quarantine Log #2"
notepad_content = "[b]Quarantine Log / Orange Alert Level[/b]

After the first wave, the interference signals haven't decreased.
They are converging at the same point and forming a new energy core.

Hypotheses:
1. Eliminating subunits triggered the \"Controller\".
2. Once energy is fully gathered, it will manifest a boss-level entity.
3. Field testers must prepare for an attack many times heavier than before.

Advice:
- Upgrade your gear before the next round.
- Maintain distance when the boss begins its phase.
- Keep moving; enemies will surround you quickly.

— System Surveillance Division"
notepad_event_target = "second_notepad"

